__ Cantrip: Bubble ___________________________ Cost: 10 ______________________

Use:   cantrip bubble                          Material Component: none
Use:   C bubble

The cantrip bubble is a minor magic of the spheres of alteration/summoning.  
When cast, a small but solid sphere of blue light appears in the hand of
the caster.  These bubbles have a duration of between four to six hours.
The light of the bubble is enough to illuminate the immediate area.
